{"id":217740,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/global-voices-新加坡：国会议员遭党内开除，触发补选战火/","date":"2012-03-27T05:17:59Z","modified":"2012-03-27T05:17:59Z","title":"Global Voices | 新加坡：国会议员遭党内开除，触发补选战火","content":"<p><p>国会议员饶欣龙爆发婚外情疑云后，所属的新加坡反对党“工人党”<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/the-workers-party/expulsion-of-yaw-shin-leong-from-party-membership/308456432537030/\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/the-workers-party/expulsion-of-yaw-shin-leong-from-party-membership/308456432537030/\">开除</a>其党籍，因而引发新加坡后港区的单选区国会议员补选。</p>\n<p>先前，饶欣龙和工人党处理这件绯闻的态度遭人<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/02/13/singapore-citizens-discuss-politicians-extramarital-scandal/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/02/13/singapore-citizens-discuss-politicians-extramarital-scandal/\">批评</a>，因为拒绝回应或是谈起这些谣言。工人党则以饶欣龙不负责任的理由，将他从党内除名。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>饶欣龙多次被指控私生活不检点，对于迟迟不向党内和后港区的居民做出任何关于绯闻的解释，饶欣龙已经辜负了党内和人民对他的信任及期望。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img title=\"Yaw Shin Leong\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/600_yawshinleong-375x187.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"187\" /></p>\n<p>对于很少有机会投票的新加坡公民（由于执政党一党独大）在这么短的期间，经历了2011年<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/28/singapore-elects-new-president/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/28/singapore-elects-new-president/\">总统</a>和议员<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/05/09/postscript-to-singapore-elections/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/05/09/postscript-to-singapore-elections/\">大选</a>，以及即将到来的议员补选，都感到非常兴奋。推特上很快就出现后港区补选的话题标记<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23hougangbyelection/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23hougangbyelection/\">#hougangbyelection</a>，集结了新加坡人民对于即将在后港区举行的议员竞选的热烈讨论。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/RealSingaporean/status/169740057731801088/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/RealSingaporean/status/169740057731801088/\">@RealSingaporean</a>：假如有选票的新加坡人都参与后港区的议员补选，就可以知道有多少人是支持执政的人民行动党了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/adesabrina/status/169717644994420737/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/adesabrina/status/169717644994420737/\">@adesabrina</a>：我想我可以听到某一政党开香槟庆祝的声音了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/talkkok/status/169727013005955072/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/talkkok/status/169727013005955072/\">@talkkok</a>：根据今年的新闻，我已经可以想像人民行动党在2016年大选，会对工人党做如何的谴责了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Ee_Justin/status/169737568773087232/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/Ee_Justin/status/169737568773087232/\">@Ee Justin</a>：工人党对决人民行动党，希望不要有其他的政党出来分散选票了。这次的选举，结果可能再次令人出乎意料吗？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>SGPolitics的Ng E-Jayy在脸书上<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/ngejay/posts/387182484628885\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ngejay/posts/387182484628885\">赞扬</a>工人党此次所采取的行动：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>四天前，我曾讲过，饶欣龙议员不是要对绯闻事件做出解释，就是得辞去职务。既然他两个都没做，工人党做了一个正确的决定，执行权 利开除他的党籍，我对工人党深感赞同。这件丑闻因为工人党果断的行动，终于可以平息。同时，工人党也展现了它的勇气、远见以及诚正。工人党，做得好！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>然而，也有人质疑，工人党采取开除党籍的作法，不是为了展现负责任和政党透明化：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/ctham/status/169718561487593472/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/ctham/status/169718561487593472/\">@ctham</a>：只因为没有解释私生活行为就开除其党籍，只是维护工人党的权宜之计，仅仅是为了平息舆论，而不是政党负责任的表现。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Yenrong\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE%E5%91%98%E9%81%AD%E5%85%9A%E5%86%85%E5%BC%80%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A5%E9%80%89%E6%88%98%E7%81%AB&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F27%2F10691%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><spa